response.overview: It starts with an innocent smile and maybe a shy wink, but what happens after that is a mystery! Imagine a person that can satisfy men and women alike, leaving them mesmerized without any recollection of a description or gender! So hang around for the surprise ending! A full length XXX rated feature starring Jon Vincent, Brigitte Aime, Rod Garetto, Sharon Kane, Bill Marlowe, Cord Colby, and Karen Dior as the "Bi Intruder."
response.title: The Bi Intruder
